snippet.title: Elements - Open-world Adventure RPG - Steam Trailer
snippet.description:
Elements Kickstarter is launching soon. Follows really help :) https://tinyurl.com/elementskickstarter
Find links to all of our socials on our website https://www.findthestones.com
You can wishlist Elements here https://store.steampowered.com/app/1468110/Elements/
Come join our discord https://discord.gg/psFZzqgB6r to give me feedback on how to make the game great.
Elements is a beautiful open-world adventure. Unlock magic and mystery as you search for elemental stones. I have been working Elements as a solo dev since June 2021. The feedback and support I have received from the community is amazing. Thank you!
